metadata.name: Blaze Camp NFT #2
metadata.description: Blaze Camp NFT is a collection of 1,500 Phoenix Bird avatars living in the ETHEREUM Blockchain. Holders of a Blaze Camp NFT will have free access to all BLAZE CAMP Online programming, BLAZE CAMP challenges, BLAZE CAMP GYMs when opened, and much more.   We are bringing together those that are passionate about fitness in web3 in order to build the first WEB3 enabled GYM starting in MIAMI, FL and projecting to franchise or license from there on to the world.   #CHASEFIRE
